aott/analysis/type_analysis/devirtualization.runa
Virtual Call Devirtualization Module for AOTT Performance

This module provides virtual call devirtualization for the Runa AOTT system including:
- Virtual method table analysis
- Class hierarchy analysis
- Type-based devirtualization
- Profile-guided devirtualization
- Speculative devirtualization with guards
- Interface method resolution
- Multiple inheritance handling
- Dynamic type checking optimization
- Inline cache management
- Polymorphic inline cache (PIC) optimization
- Megamorphic call site handling
- Virtual dispatch elimination
- Method resolution caching
- Cross-tier devirtualization
- Devirtualization safety verification
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

